<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Jun 2026 02:07:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Tether 以太币价值的短暂翻转让加密货币面临现实检验</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/tether-usdt-stablecoin-briefly-overtakes-ethereum-eth-in-market-value</link><description>上周末的几个小时内，Tether 的 USDT 稳定币变得比以太币更有价值。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQRw1bDn8B30/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 11:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/tether-usdt-stablecoin-briefly-overtakes-ethereum-eth-in-market-value</guid></item><item><title>比特币抄底者关注人工智能狂热和 SpaceX IPO</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/bitcoin-bottom-hunters-are-eyeing-up-ai-frenzy-and-spacex-ipo</link><description>比特币本周从 60,000 美元以下的绝望深渊中反弹，重新点燃了华尔街熟悉的仪式：试图触底。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iK0t80Pd3k5o/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 14:38:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/bitcoin-bottom-hunters-are-eyeing-up-ai-frenzy-and-spacex-ipo</guid></item><item><title>世界杯 100 亿美元的博彩热潮推动市场“游戏化”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/world-cup-s-10-billion-betting-boom-fuels-market-gamification</link><description>世界杯预计将成为地球上最大的体育赛事。这也可能成为该行业迄今为止将全球体育赛事转变为投机交易引擎的最大机会。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSRIleu54gW4/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 16:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-12/world-cup-s-10-billion-betting-boom-fuels-market-gamification</guid></item><item><title>班克曼-弗里德的赦免重新开启了痛苦的加密记忆</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-11/bankman-fried-s-pardon-bid-reopens-painful-crypto-memories</link><description>对于许多加密货币领域的长期参与者来说，SBF 的要求令人恼火。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqF8f6pRIaYw/v4/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-11/bankman-fried-s-pardon-bid-reopens-painful-crypto-memories</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 加密货币交易员押注 2.2 万亿美元估值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/spacex-crypto-traders-are-betting-on-a-2-2-trillion-valuation</link><description>加密货币交易员正在忽略 SpaceX 的预期 IPO 价格，并在埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的火箭、卫星和人工智能公司上市前给予其更高的估值。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKgq4ftSvO2c/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 14:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/spacex-crypto-traders-are-betting-on-a-2-2-trillion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利将与欧尔班相反，将加密货币交易合法化</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/hungary-to-decriminalize-crypto-trading-in-reversal-from-orban</link><description>匈牙利将取消加密货币交易的刑罪化，扭转前领导人欧尔班·维克托 (Viktor Orban) 实行的限制。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCZl6IiYg2Rs/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 10:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/hungary-to-decriminalize-crypto-trading-in-reversal-from-orban</guid></item><item><title>安德森霍洛维茨支持华尔街巨头使用的区块链</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/andreessen-horowitz-backs-blockchain-used-by-wall-street-giants</link><description>随着华尔街加速关注使用加密货币背后的技术来处理传统资产，区块链建设者 Digital Asset Holdings LLC 在由 Andreessen Horowitz 的主要加密货币基金领投的新一轮融资中筹集了 3.55 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iikbQ6yPtjn4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/andreessen-horowitz-backs-blockchain-used-by-wall-street-giants</guid></item><item><title>日本采取类似股票监管方式来监管加密货币以推动市场增长</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/japan-moves-to-regulate-crypto-like-stocks-in-market-growth-push</link><description>日本议会准备通过立法，将加密货币纳入与股票相同的监管框架下，此举旨在扩大数字资产的获取范围。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8rO5LTKUbio/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 06:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/japan-moves-to-regulate-crypto-like-stocks-in-market-growth-push</guid></item></channel></rss>